__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

âœ¨ 3. Ar-Rahmaan aur Ar-Raheem ka Farq
Ar-Rahmaan â†’ Allah ki woh Rehmat jo sab par aam hai (Momineen aur Ghair-Momineen dono par). Jaise rozi, hawa, paani, sehat, zindagi dena.
Ar-Raheem â†’ Allah ki woh khaas Rehmat jo sirf Imaan walon ke liye hai. Jaise hidayat, sukoon-e-dil, maghfirat, aur Jannat.

âš–ï¸ Samajhne ke liye:
Ar-Rahmaan = Duniya me sabko milne wali Rehmat.
Ar-Raheem = Aakhirat me imaan walon ke liye khaas Rehmat.

__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

âœ¨ 4. Sifat ka Asar (Impact)
Ar-Raheem ka matlab yeh hai ke Allah apne nek bandon ka saath nahi chhorta.
Duniya me unhe sukoon, rahnumai, aur madad deta hai.
Aakhirat me unko Jannat, maafi aur naimat ata karega.

__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

âœ¨ 5. Amal me Kya Seekhein?
Allah ki Rehmat par Bharosa rakhein.
Ghalti ho jaye to yaad karein: Allah Ar-Raheem hai, bas tauba karni hai.
Rehamdil banna seekhein.
Nabi ï·º ne farmaya: â€œJo logon par reham nahi karta, Allah us par reham nahi karega.â€
Duaon me is Naam ka zikr karna.
â€œYa Ar-Raheem, hum par apni khaas Rehmat nazil farma, humein Jannat ke mustahiq bana.â€

__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

âœ¨ 6. Daily Reflection / Sochnay ki Baat
Main apni zindagi me kitna rehamdil hoon?
Kya main apni ghaltiyon ke bawajood Allah se maafi aur Rehmat ki umeed rakhta hoon?
Kya main Allah ki is sifaat ka aaks apni family, dost aur mohtaj logon ke saath rawaiye me dikhata hoon?

